Installing:
    - Copy Network.Link interface in model.xml into /etc/comar/model.xml
    - Copy these files to /usr/share/PolicyKit/policy/
        - policy/tr.org.pardus.comar.network.link.policy
    - Stop COMAR
    - Register scripts:
        # hav register net_tools Network.Link scripts/net-tools.py
        # hav register wireless_tools Network.Link scripts/wireless-tools.py
        # hav register ppp Network.Link scripts/ppp.py
    - Have fun :)
